5:
So the plan is to take down the
bases of a criminal organization?
9:
Yep. Turns out they're a real slimy
group that abuses orphans.
14:
Tch, those are some seriously
messed up folks.
18:
They're taking advantage of
Halloween to put some nasty
schemes into action.
22:
The Guild Knights are doing all they
can, but we figured it couldn't hurt to
get even more hands on deck.
That's where you all come in!
24:
You'll be out patrolling and securing
a bunch of enemy strongholds!
28:
We're counting on you to help make
this a Halloween safe for everyone!
34:
There's a lot more strongholds than I
thought there'd be... We're being
split into teams, right?
38:
...Ah, I'm actually in a different party
than you two—
47:
*sigh* I can't believe I got paired up
with some wimpy-looking girl. This
sucks.
51:
Oh, I guess this m-means you're my
partner... It's nice to meet you.
54:
...Hmph, the rumors were clearly
exaggerated. You're nowhere near
as tough as they made you sound.
56:
Sometimes I can't tell friend from foe
when I get worked up, so stay out of
my way. Or don't. It's up to you,
ahaha!
63:
There is ZERO chemistry going on.
Are you sure you'll be fine with her?
67:
Y-yeah... I'm used to verbal abuse
like that. It's nothing I haven't heard
before.
72:
Heh, she has no idea who she's
messing with. You should show her
what you're really made of.
76:
We'll swing by later to help out once
we've finished securing our
locations.
82:
Th-thank you! I'll do what I c-can so
you don't have to do extra work.
88:
Oh! That's a lot of powerful looking
enemies!
91:
U-um... How many am I allowed to
take for myself?
94: Huh? What kinda question is that?
95:
Just focus on staying out of my way.
I can take one of those guys by
myself, easy.
97:
Oh, but if I start to get too wild, you
better stop me.
99:
I LOVE tearing guys like these apart. I
get so into it that I start to forget my
surroundings.
106:
We don't really have too much
time... Shall we get started?
118: Do you have any treats? No? Then...
131:
Y-you DARE mess with us? Don't
think we're gonna let you off easy!
135:
Ohhh, I can't get enough of the way
your face twists in anger! Like a
simple-minded animal!
140:
Not bad, little lady... But this is the
end of the line for you!
142:
D-don't get the wrong idea! I just
happened to mess up this time—
147:
You can still stand, can't you? So get
up! I'm not satisfied yet!
152: Do you like it here? Or here?
160:
Melmyna, sorry we took so long!
How—
169:
Ohhh, I love seeing the fear in your
eyes... Keep screaming like that! Yes!
173:
Hehehehe! There's no running from
me! You still haven't learned your
lesson yet, after all!
176:
Anyone! Who! Abuses! Children!
Should! Repent! Hehe!
183:
...It's a good thing we showed up to
help out.
187:
Yeah... We better stop her before
they lose their minds.
